Citation.sTitle: Vapor Pressures and Enthalpies of Vaporization of a Series of the Linear Aliphatic Nitriles.
Citation.sAbstract: Vapour pressures and the molar enthalpies of vaporization of the linear aliphatic nitriles C7 - C17 have been determined by the transpiration method. Kovat`s indices of these Compounds were measured by capillary gas-chromatography. A linear correlation of enthalpies of vaporization at T = 298.15 K of the nitriles studied with the Kovats indices has been found.
